This Digital Content License Agreement (the "Agreement") is entered into by and between AdThoughtsGlobal ("Company," "we," "us," or "our") and you, the individual or entity accessing or interacting with any digital content, work, file, or idea (collectively referred to as "Content") provided by AdThoughtsGlobal through any means, including but not limited to websites, applications, software, or electronic communications.

