You expressly agree and acknowledge the following restrictions:

a. No Copying or Reproduction: You shall not copy, reproduce, distribute, publish, display, or create derivative works based on any AdThoughtsGlobal Content, in whole or in part, without explicit written permission from AdThoughtsGlobal.

